<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0">
        <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
        <title>New Task</title>
    </head>
    <body style="width: 80%; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
        <div style="height:10%; display:flex; gap:7%; align-items:center;">
            <img src = 'https://www.vfactor.ru/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/logo-02.png' style="object-fit: contain; height: 37px; width: auto; ">
            <h1 style="font-size: 37px; text-align: center" >DIGITAL DESIGN NOTIFICATION</h1>
        </div>
        <p style="font-style: italic; font-size: 25px; margin-top: 45px;">Hi, ${name}!</p>
        <p style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 25px;">There is new task for you!</p>
        <p style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 25px;">Task name: <span style="font-weight: 300;"> ${taskName} </span></p>
        <p style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 25px;">Task description: <span style="font-weight: 300;"> ${taskDescription} </span></p>
        <p style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 25px;">Task deadline: <span style="font-weight: 300;">${taskDeadline} </span></p>
        <p style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 25px;">Send to: <span style="font-weight: 300;">${sendTo}</span></p>
        <p style="font-style: italic; font-size: 25px;">Best regards, <br> DigitalDesign!</p>
    </body>
</html>